      "rationale": "N=11 constructs tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: n=6, Lab B: n=5). All constructs from production lots with full material and dimensional traceability. Coefficient of variation in experimental stiffness = 3.1%, yield force = 4.7%, confirming low inter-specimen variability consistent with production-quality hardware."
