      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single quasi-static loading rate (5 mm/min) per ASTM F1717 protocol. Saline bath at 37°C used in Lab A only; Lab B tested in ambient air. Rate dependence and environmental effects on titanium alloy mechanical response not characterised within this validation study. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this gap is acknowledged and accepted at Medium risk level per COU risk determination."
